# ── Wix Headless ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your Headless OAuth Client ID.
# Until it's set, the app runs on built-in demo data (nothing breaks).
#
# Where to find it: WIX_SETUP.md, or:
#   Wix dashboard → Settings → Headless → OAuth apps → your app → Client ID
NEXT_PUBLIC_WIX_CLIENT_ID=

# ── Seed script only (scripts/seed-wix-events.mjs) ───────────────────────────
# Needed ONLY if you want to auto-create the 8 sample events via the API.
# Create an API key at https://manage.wix.com/account/api-keys with the
# "Wix Events" permission, and copy your site's metaSiteId.
WIX_API_KEY=
WIX_SITE_ID=
